definitions.definition: A wine from the area around the Rhine .
examples: He insists on drinking Rhenish from a stein!

definitions.definition: The linguistic varieties spoken in the Rhineland , a continuum between traditional dialects and regional forms of Standard German .

main_definition: A wine from the area around the Rhine .
